{"tid":576271,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"俾想考DSE中英嘅人建議","createTime":"2018-02-28T18:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T02:30:15.000Z","uid":113733,"like":19,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5c16b36d39a12d5401b74d897b293e1443b1ec6c","tid":576271,"uid":113733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:10:39.000Z","msg":"如果你係想考返靚個成績<br />\n除非你本身三或以下想去四<br />\n五或以上嘅機會極微<br />\n語文考試已經係講緊答題技巧<br />\n最重分嘅卷一同三一定要經過好多操練<br />\n基本上已經唔係好關你嘅造詣 <br />\n你自問自己幾多年冇考過呢啲試？<br />\nHighlight 自己中大港大中英文系可以收返<br />\n你識多一兩隻字都唔會幫到好多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於Oral 方面<br />\n佢係睇成組表現評分 <br />\n佢計嗰十幾分係救梗人哋其他卷嘅失分<br />\n大家都係為求過到關<br />\n你當年又何嘗唔係？ <br />\n玩？玩你老母。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家可以理性啲<br />\n唔好盲目仇視<br />\n錯嘅係制度本身<br />\n我哋都係被逼嘅參與者<br />\n制度需要改變<br />\n但唔會係用呢種方式<br />\n我哋組團去幫陳局長雛菊開苞唔係更有意思咩？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後<br />\n希望帶住「我考唔到所以都唔會俾你哋考到」嘅廢柴、垃圾、敗類不得好死，長命百歲、百病叢生、永不超生。<br />\n我亦都祝福用心去考嘅人。"},{"pid":"a25bfca940eb9bce500ac504636a30203fa2da71","tid":576271,"uid":113733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc8cc7f798c5d032acbec1fcbf7a4eb3fed048a","tid":576271,"uid":113733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f14f6a5d6efc19eb2617ca21fbbb31523110d3a","tid":576271,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:21:59.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"57da2b9d8f7fae56eda0d55515af77e3512ae9ac","tid":576271,"uid":12185,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:26:44.000Z","msg":"其實條curve係分開"},{"pid":"ef7bf40f5088c669cae9c53ee2f548f02a5b5dc2","tid":576271,"uid":113733,"lik